description: I started hunting near a shopping mall but things didn't go well at first. No one was willing to talk, so I decided to change location. While I was waiting for a tram that would get me somewhere more promising, a guy with a suitcase stood next to me on the platform. He was pretty and I immediately got interested. I switched my camera on and approached him. He was a bit nervous about me at first but my charm calmed him down eventually. I learned he worked in IT and went to Prague for a little vacation. IT guys are usually hard to convince but this one had to be new at the job because my offers worked quite well on him. It didn't take very long before we ended up at his hotel room. He was just stunning. His muscular frame made me incredibly horny, and I went absolutely crazy over his huge boner.
title: Czech Hunter 392
